Description: Access data and analysis tools from the DISCO (immunesinglecell.com)
    single-cell RNA-seq database. Provides functions for querying sample metadata,
    downloading expression data, running integration, automated cell-type annotation
    (CELLiD), differential expression, and gene set enrichment.
